Package de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest Description

This package provides classes used to produce the JSON and XML outputs for RESTful services related to both projects and system database schemas. For OpenInfRA there exists two self updating API documentations available via the following URLs:
  • http://localhost:8080/openinfra_core/rest/application.wadl (Standard XML-based (WADL) API documentation provided by Jersey.)
  • http://localhost:8080/openinfra_core/rest/application.html (HTML representation/transformation of the aforementioned WADL.)
Moreover, helper classes are also provided.
Author:
BTU DBIS
